title="Jon Sterling">Jon Sterling</fr:link></fr:author></fr:authors></fr:frontmatter><fr:mainmatter><fr:p>Let <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {K}]]></fr:tex> be a 2-category with a terminal object <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {1}]]></fr:tex>; a 1-cell <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathbf {1}\xrightarrow {p}E]]></fr:tex> in <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[\mathcal {K}]]></fr:tex> need not be full.</fr:p>
 
   
